div.summary:
The following number of passengers were carried from stations on the
                    Cumberland Valley Railroad during the last fiscal year: Greencastle, 13,104;
                    Chambersburg, 33,464; Scotland, 2,045; Shippensburg, 16,768. The following
                    stations shipped the following pounds in freight: Greencastle, 29,554,845;
                    Chambersburg, 53,858,239; Shippensburg, 39,002,826.
